latestPosts.caption:
“you’re very strong”
i don’t know how many times i’ve heard the phrase “you’re the strongest person that i know!”
and as flattering it may be, it is sometimes very exhausting… just that. maybe i never wanted to be this strong. maybe i also wanted to sit down and just cry and do nothing. but there was never room for that.
right now that my cat has gone missing i’m spending the hardest times of my life; but again i have to be strong. while all i wanna do is just crash down and crawl under a blanket and never come out, but of course there’s no way for that. 
so i’ll hold my guards up, put the mask on, and keep on going.
In a world full of noise, I’ll take silence — and a fit that speaks for me 🐈‍⬛🤎
